value



The property value to copy

Hash don't consider floating point precision. So even if two values equality return true, they can have different hash value. Property::Valuev1(1.0f);
Property::Valuev2(1.0000001192092896f);//1.0f+FLT_EPSILON
assert(v1==v2);//true
assert(v1.GetHash()==v2.GetHash());//false,becauseoffloatingpointprecisionissue.


